   Northwest Region Construction Information

   The Northwest Region is made up of Island, King, eastern Pierce, San
   Juan, Skagit, Snohomish, and Whatcom counties. The following regional
   construction information is available:
     * Construction Lane Closures: A daily updated report describing where
       lanes will be closed due to construction.
     * Construction Activity Update Report: Check here for a weekly status
       report of the major state highway construction projects.

